====Usage notes====
{{lang|ja|燈}} was in the ''tōyō kanji'' list from 1946. It was used interchangeably with its simpler variant {{m|ja|灯}}. In 1981, it was replaced by {{m|ja|灯}} with the introduction of the {{ja-r|常%用%漢%字|じょう%よう% かん%じ}}. At the same time, the ''tōyō kanji'' {{lang|ja|燈}} has been repurposed as a ''jinmeiyō'' variant of a ''jōyō kanji''.

